<Layout title="The Perno Family">
	<main>
		<h1>Eliza's First Birthday</h1>
		<p>They grow up so fast! It seems like just last week that Eliza was born. Now she's turning one! We're so excited to celebrate with you. Please join us for a fun-filled day of food, games, friends, and family.</p>
		
		<h2>When?</h2>
		<p>
			<strong>Date: </strong>
			Saturday, October 7th, 2023
			<br/>
			<strong>Time: </strong>
			1:00pm - 4:00pm
		</p>
		
		<h2>Where?</h2>
		<address>
			Alstede Farm<br/>
			1 Alstede Farms Ln<br />
		  Chester, NJ 07930
		</address>
		<p style="margin-bottom: 1rem">
			<a href="https://www.alstedefarms.com/">Visit their Website</a>
		</p>
		<p>
			<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Alstede+Farms/@40.779056,-74.713821,14z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x89c3990b3264ed17:0xd043541046a9664f!8m2!3d40.7789241!4d-74.7137164!16s%2Fg%2F1td7_0ft?hl=en-US&entry=ttu">Get Directions</a>
		</p>
		
		<h2>What can we bring?</h2>
		<p>
			Please refrain from buying or giving presents. The world doesn't need more plastic waste, and she's perfectly happy with what she has. However, if you're inclined, please consider contributing to Eliza's college fund (link coming soon), or consider donating to <a href="/donate">one of these charities</a>.
		</p>
	</main>
</Layout>

